            "value": "<p>You create a powerful blast of air and a loud peal of thunder, dealing [[/r 2d6 #bludgeoning]] bludgeoning damage and [[/r 2d6 #sonic]] sonic damage. Each creature in the area must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected<strong>.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is<br />Deafened for 1 hour.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> Increase each type of damage by [[/r 2d6]] and the area by 5 feet.</p>"
